 cinema itself. This is where the movies’ long love affair with the grammar of time started.” <strong>Rahul Desai</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>“It’s hard to think of a more perfect film about the focal role of storytelling in the construction of human society.” <strong>Vigen Galstyan</strong></p>\r\n","quote":null,"credits":{"director":"Akira Kurosawa","producer":"Jinkichi Minoru, Sojiro Motoki","writer":"Akira Kurosawa, Shinobu Hashimoto","featuring":"Toshiro Mifune, Machiko Kyo, Takashi Shimura"},"year":"1950","nameAndYear":"Rashomon (1950)","links":{"player":"https://player.bfi.org.uk/subscription/film/watch-rashomon-1950-online","southbank":""},"player":{"url":"https://player.bfi.org.uk/subscription/film/watch-rashomon-1950-online","cta":"https://player.bfi.org.uk/subscribe/5647","pillar":"subscription","price":0,"duration":0},"performances":[],"tags":["BFI Player"],"productionCountries":"Japan","runningTime":83,"sightAndSound":{"results":[{"position":41,"tied":true,"category":"critics"},{"position":20,"tied":true,"category":"directors"}],"voters":null},"products":[]},{"uuid":"4f761796-31a3-5c18-a868-c589d3e2b126","image":{"base":"https://core-cms.bfi.org.uk/sites/default/files/","relative":"2021-09/the-adventures-of-prince-achmed-1926-princess-green-tinted.jpg","main":"https://core-cms.bfi.org.uk/sites/default/files/styles/responsive/public/2021-09/the-adventures-of-prince-achmed-1926-princess-green-tinted.jpg/1920x1080-cropped/the-adventures-of-prince-achmed-1926-princess-green-tinted.jpg","thumb":"https://core-cms.bfi.org.uk/sites/default/files/styles/responsive/public/2021-09/the-adventures-of-prince-achmed-1926-princess-green-tinted.jpg/960x540-cropped/the-adventures-of-prince-achmed-1926-princess-green-tinted.jpg","preload":"https://core-cms.bfi.org.uk/sites/default/files/styles/responsive/public/2021-09/the-adventures-of-prince-achmed-1926-princess-green-tinted.jpg/96x54-cropped/the-adventures-of-prince-achmed-1926-princess-green-tinted.jpg","altText":null},"na